Package: screenpilot
Version: 0.3.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, ddcutil, brightnessctl
Maintainer: Mayank Pratap
Description: Unified brightness and contrast controls for connected displays
 ScreenPilot controls laptop backlights and DDC/CI external monitors from one
 lightweight native GTK application.

